Xavier Leroy


[English version:]

It is our pleasure to announce the release of Caml Light version 0.71
for Macintosh.

The main novelty of this version is its internationalization: editing
the resources of the application you may change the language used by
Caml to output error messages (default languages: english and french).

host: ftp.inria.fr (192.93.2.54)
directory: lang/caml-light

url: ftp://ftp.inria.fr/lang/caml-light/

Bug reports should be mailed to caml-light@pauillac.inria.fr.

Damien Doligez
Pierre Weis
Xavier Leroy




